HACKERS HOWTO
-------------

Here are the basics.

Directories:

lordsawar
    - po           // contains localization files      			
    - dat	   // contains various data-files
    - doc	   // contains some documentation on the game
    - src   	   // Game sources
    - src/server   // Client & Server code (not used)
    - src/gui      // Graphical Interface sources
    - src/editor   // contains various editors
    

Important files for beginners:

    - lordsawar/doc/Internals
    - lordsawar/doc/Savefile
    - And all of the header files
